 15th F Amb second 14th third . Mail from all report again gone to the bottom Friday 13.7.17 Spent the morn on the car collect 14 Brigad sick in around Mailli . New Sgt arriv here to-day in lieu of Sgt Thompson who has transfer to 3rd AGH. At Abbevill . Saturday 14.7.17 Big day in the French Town . Had leav grant but turn it down Sunday 15.7.17 Church Servic at 9 Am . Afternoon 3 cricket match play , won two lost 1 . Rig 's pal , N.C . Roper came to see me spent the even . Monday 16.7.17
